<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ب ط أ:</span> <span class="c2">(بَطُؤَ)</span> بِالضَّمِّ <span class="c2">(بُطْئًا)</span> بِضَمِّ الْبَاءِ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(بَطِيءٌ)</span> بِالْمَدِّ وَ <span class="c2">(أَبْطَأَ)</span> فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(مُبْطِئٌ)</span> وَلَا تَقُلْ: أَبْطَيْتُ وَمَا <span class="c2">(أَبْطَأَ)</span> بِكَ وَ <span class="c2">(بَطَّأَ)</span> بِكَ مُشَدَّدًا بِمَعْنًى. وَ <span class="c2">(تَبَاطَأَ)</span> فِي مَسِيرِهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>